reviewText: Great movie for learning. My kids love it!
Purchased for a 1yr old and he loves this movie
Sesame Street seems to be a thing of the past.  They are all old friends of my family. These are two of the best DVDs for toddlers sold today!
This  video is a favorite of my children. They love the catchy tunes, and enjoy singing along. It's a fun way to help preschoolers learn the alphabet.
